{"tid":1360812,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[召集轉貼員]用Telegram group 比最新消息給外媒記者","createTime":"2019-07-24T12:32:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T14:14:34.000Z","uid":287422,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"444b58aa20519447c75d9d24a724c911e3681043","tid":1360812,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:32:04.000Z","msg":"好多時外媒記者唔識中文，又唔識睇香港的facebook、論壇，所以報的新聞不夠深入，所以我想招人幫手做三件事：<br />\n1. 入英文telegram group，例如<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/standwithhongkong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstandwithhongkong&d=ye2s6s2DGg0XurdvegCh9a7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=517f2c72\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/standwithhongkong</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/swhkdemocracyfrontline\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fswhkdemocracyfrontline&d=ye2s6s2DGg0XurdvegCh9a7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=ca2a9d0c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/swhkdemocracyfrontline</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hkiswatching\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkiswatching&d=ye2s6s2DGg0XurdvegCh9a7%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=03e3e851\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkiswatching</a><br />\n<br />\n2. 一有新的消息就轉貼過去，再簡單翻譯，例如：<br />\n[link]<br />\n[21/7/2019] Yeun Long: white shirted armed mob attack a pregnant woman in MTR station<br />\n<br />\n譯得不好沒關係，跟得足的記者多數已經有人幫手翻譯，其他人見你譯得不好也會再譯，最重要是讓他們有一個集中地去知消息。<br />\n<br />\n重點是資料來源，因為外國記者通常會要求找當事人出來訪問去factcheck，你能找到資料來源最好，找不到也最少貼出能夠追到來源的連結。<br />\n<br />\n但請盡量只貼新聞，不要貼文宣，偶然也可以把類似的新聞集合再加簡單分析，例如撐警。說30萬但之前黑警說添馬公園只能站1.7萬人就會有用。<br />\n<br />\n網上傳聞對記者來說未必能用來做新聞，但重要點的也應該譯，但會讓他們更好理解背景，例如21/7前那篇AO出來說政府要用黑社會的，他們知道了就會有所準備。我之前譯這些資料給他們，他們也說不會嫌多。<br />\n<br />\n不夠重要的就別譯，人始終無時間看那麼多資料<br />\n<br />\n3. 找所有有報導香港的外國記者資料，邀請他們入group，通知他們我們會譯新聞給他們"},{"pid":"1448ce879c9952d87c848f1e49e947df521c13e4","tid":1360812,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:41:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f321a32d4f8d407aac18dae11b1a3d1756c5ac4d","tid":1360812,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T12:51:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e70a92bd9c8228615e67a622ba47672727cd765","tid":1360812,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T13:01:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5aaac22a166e6b1d17a13609ca6404742390a6c","tid":1360812,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T13:18:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be5a2a0d03d8143ae72a7a9363b8b38b9080b874","tid":1360812,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T13:42:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd497c8db05e88d52dca416cc4d1127f5fa435d6","tid":1360812,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T14:04:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4be19773ad59c3e537a6b97a3fc47da86d64751c","tid":1360812,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T14:14:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}